==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[ki-]]'' (interrogative and relative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-el]]'' (correlative suffix of manner or degree)

===Correlative===
'''kiel'''
# [[how]] (interrogative and relative correlative of manner or degree)
#: Like other interrogative and relative correlatives, '''kiel''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Kiel''' ajn'' thus means ''[[however]]''.

